Pre-Game Insights: Albion Rrahmani, a forward for Sparta Praga, expressed his desire to play for Kosovo against Romania and stated that the Kosovar team is well-prepared for the match.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match between Kosovo and Romania will take place on September 6, 2024, at 21:45, as part of the first stage of Group 2 in League C of the Nations League. The game can be followed live on the Digi Sport website or through the Digi Sport app by Digi Romania subscribers.
